# Sync Before Test Launch

Before launching or testing `trl.exe`, sync the active runtime artifacts from
`patches/trl_legend_ffp/proxy/` into `A:\SteamLibrary\steamapps\common\Tomb Raider Legend`.

Use:

`powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File "patches/trl_legend_ffp/sync_runtime_to_game.ps1"`

If launching as part of the same step, use:

`powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File "patches/trl_legend_ffp/sync_runtime_to_game.ps1" -Launch`

This keeps the live game directory current with the working proxy folder.

Never assume repo-side changes affect the running game until the runtime files
have been synced into the game directory.
